    <p><strong>Combi oven prices in India in 2026 range from approximately ₹3.5 lakh for a basic 6-tray electric combi oven to over ₹35 lakh for a premium 20-tray Rational iCombi Pro unit.</strong> A combi oven — short for combination oven — is arguably the single most versatile piece of commercial kitchen equipment you can buy. It combines three cooking modes in one unit: dry convection heat, pure steam, and a combination of both. Whether you run a hotel banquet kitchen, a cloud kitchen, a QSR chain, or a hospital cafeteria, a combi oven can replace multiple standalone appliances and dramatically simplify your cooking workflow.</p>

    <p>This comprehensive guide covers everything you need to know about buying a combi oven in India: how they work, which brands are available, detailed pricing by capacity and brand, running cost analysis, installation requirements, and a clear decision framework to help you decide if a combi oven is right for your kitchen.</p>

