    <p>This is the most common question we get from Indian buyers: "Why should I spend ₹8–15 lakh on a combi oven when I can buy a <a href="/blog/bakery-oven-price-india">convection oven for ₹50,000–₹2 lakh</a>?" Here is a thorough breakdown.</p>

