        <tr><td>Touchscreen / Smart Controls</td><td>Rarely</td><td>Standard on mid-range and above</td></tr>
        <tr><td>Self-Cleaning</td><td>Manual cleaning</td><td>Automatic self-cleaning cycle</td></tr>
        <tr><td>Core Temperature Probe</td><td>Rarely included</td><td>Standard (multi-point probes on premium models)</td></tr>
        <tr><td>Typical Price (10-tray, India)</td><td>₹1,20,000 – ₹2,00,000</td><td>₹8,00,000 – ₹19,00,000</td></tr>
